{"data":[{"id":564652214,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":307595822,"title":"高中生对哥德巴赫猜想的证明有哪些错误？","question_type":"normal","created":1546272354,"updated_time":1546301579,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/307595822","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"56e87b9fc2532c536506ecec965ee2e0","url_token":"zhang-yao-nan-1","name":"无名","avatar_url":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-a214fb329c41fe31333b93a066355377_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-a214fb329c41fe31333b93a066355377_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/56e87b9fc2532c536506ecec965ee2e0","user_type":"people","headline":"know nothing","badge":[],"gender":1,"is_advertiser":false,"follower_count":910,"is_followed":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/564652214","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1546403201,"updated_time":1546409325,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":11,"comment_count":1,"is_sticky":false,"admin_closed_comment":false,"comment_permission":"all","can_comment":{"reason":"","status":true},"reshipment_settings":"allowed","content":"\u003cp\u003e好想说一句“实名反对所有回答”啊（雾）\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e但是确实很失望。这个问题下还稍微好一点，之前的问题下攻击“负质数”的、说是假设猪有翅膀所以猪会飞的看得更加尴尬。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e【更正：看到了一个似乎正确的回答，虽然说得不太清楚 \u003ca href=\"https://www.zhihu.com/question/307595822/answer/563884230\" class=\"internal\"\u003e高中生对哥德巴赫猜想的证明有哪些错误？\u003c/a\u003e】\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e这位高中生确实写得很不规范，但理解他真正想说什么并找出错误，应该也没那么困难吧。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003e（主要引起误会的应该就是“若-1是质数...”那个地方吧）\u003c/b\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e下文是我的回答：\u003c/p\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/53756921\" data-draft-node=\"block\" data-draft-type=\"link-card\" data-image=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-3784baee92c59340ff827ba5cce5a19d_180x120.jpg\" data-image-width=\"640\" data-image-height=\"404\" class=\"internal\"\u003e无名：为什么知乎用户“证明”关于哥德巴赫猜想的证明是错误的\u003c/a\u003e\u003cp\u003e他真正的错误在于混淆了\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://www.zhihu.com/equation?tex=%28%5Cexists+x%2C++R%28x%29+%29+%5Crightarrow+S\" alt=\"(\\exists x,  R(x) ) \\rightarrow S\" eeimg=\"1\"\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e和\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://www.zhihu.com/equation?tex=%5Cexists+x%2C++%28R%28x%29+%5Crightarrow+S%29\" alt=\"\\exists x,  (R(x) \\rightarrow S)\" eeimg=\"1\"\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e举个例子就是，“存在一只猫，它是橘猫”推出“我有猫”显然是假命题\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e存在一只猫，“它是橘猫”能推出“我有猫”却是个真命题——找只英短就可以了，反正假前提可以推出任何结论。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003e“把-1归入质数”并不是不行\u003c/b\u003e：令广义质数集合\u003cimg src=\"https://www.zhihu.com/equation?tex=Q%27+%3D+P+%5Ccup+%5C%7B-1%5C%7D\" alt=\"Q' = P \\cup \\{-1\\}\" eeimg=\"1\"\u003e,以及对应的\u003cimg src=\"https://www.zhihu.com/equation?tex=A%27+%3D+%5C%7Bx%7C+x%3Dp_1%2Bp_2%2C+p_1%2Cp_2+%5Cin+Q%27%5C%7D\" alt=\"A' = \\{x| x=p_1+p_2, p_1,p_2 \\in Q'\\}\" eeimg=\"1\"\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003e“若..则1不是质数”也并不一定自带矛盾\u003c/b\u003e：\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e原命题\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e对于某一广义质数集合 \u003cimg src=\"https://www.zhihu.com/equation?tex=Q_x+%5Csupseteq+P\" alt=\"Q_x \\supseteq P\" eeimg=\"1\"\u003e 及其对应的广义质数和集合 \u003cimg src=\"https://www.zhihu.com/equation?tex=A_x+%3D+%5C%7Bx%7C+x%3Dp_1%2Bp_2%2C+p_1%2Cp_2+%5Cin+Q_x%5C%7D\" alt=\"A_x = \\{x| x=p_1+p_2, p_1,p_2 \\in Q_x\\}\" eeimg=\"1\"\u003e，若 \u003cimg src=\"https://www.zhihu.com/equation?tex=-1+%5Cin+Q_x\" alt=\"-1 \\in Q_x\" eeimg=\"1\"\u003e，则 \u003cimg src=\"https://www.zhihu.com/equation?tex=%5Cforall+n+%5Cin+%5Cmathbb%7BN%7D%5E%2B%2C+2n%5Cin+A_x\" alt=\"\\forall n \\in \\mathbb{N}^+, 2n\\in A_x\" eeimg=\"1\"\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e逆否命题\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e对于某一广义质数集合\u003cimg src=\"https://www.zhihu.com/equation?tex=Q_x+%5Csupseteq+P\" alt=\"Q_x \\supseteq P\" eeimg=\"1\"\u003e及其对应的广义质数和集合\u003cimg src=\"https://www.zhihu.com/equation?tex=A_x+%3D+%5C%7Bx%7C+x%3Dp_1%2Bp_2%2C+p_1%2Cp_2+%5Cin+Q_x%5C%7D\" alt=\"A_x = \\{x| x=p_1+p_2, p_1,p_2 \\in Q_x\\}\" eeimg=\"1\"\u003e，若\u003cimg src=\"https://www.zhihu.com/equation?tex=%5Cexists+n+%5Cin+%5Cmathbb%7BN%7D%5E%2B%2C+2n%5Cnotin+A_x\" alt=\"\\exists n \\in \\mathbb{N}^+, 2n\\notin A_x\" eeimg=\"1\"\u003e, 则\u003cimg src=\"https://www.zhihu.com/equation?tex=-1+%5Cnotin+Q_x\" alt=\"-1 \\notin Q_x\" eeimg=\"1\"\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e这个命题也真能推出他的变式一，原命题中带入\u003cimg src=\"https://www.zhihu.com/equation?tex=Q_x+%3D+Q%27\" alt=\"Q_x = Q'\" eeimg=\"1\"\u003e就能得到。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e唯一的问题在于他真没证出来（废话当然证不出来），后面对逆否命题的证明是错误的，找了只英短就想证明我有猫。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e并不是循环论证那么简单，Not even wrong的评价在这里也并不太适用\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003e事前不少人无脑支持，事后群魔乱舞，一个中二高中生的两三页胡言乱语，或成为知乎真实平均数学水平的试金石。\u003c/b\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e（其实我觉得这位高中生的数学水平再怎么还是比某自称高考数学72分的答主高不少的）\u003c/p\u003e","editable_content":"","excerpt":"好想说一句“实名反对所有回答”啊（雾）但是确实很失望。这个问题下还稍微好一点，之前的问题下攻击“负质数”的、说是假设猪有翅膀所以猪会飞的看得更加尴尬。【更正：看到了一个似乎正确的回答，虽然说得不太清楚 \u003ca href=\"https://www.zhihu.com/question/307595822/answer/563884230\" class=\"internal\"\u003e高中生对哥德巴赫猜想的证明有哪些错误？\u003c/a\u003e…","collapsed_by":"nobody","collapse_reason":"","annotation_action":[],"mark_infos":[],"relevant_info":{"is_relevant":false,"relevant_type":"","relevant_text":""},"suggest_edit":{"reason":"","status":false,"tip":"","title":"","unnormal_details":{"status":"","description":"","reason":"","reason_id":0,"note":""},"url":""},"is_labeled":false,"reward_info":{"can_open_reward":false,"is_rewardable":false,"reward_member_count":0,"reward_total_money":0,"tagline":""},"relationship":{"is_author":false,"is_authorized":false,"is_nothelp":false,"is_thanked":false,"voting":0,"upvoted_followees":[]}}],"paging":{"is_end":false,"is_start":false,"next":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/307595822/answ